_said shultz had given him an ``encouraging'' report on his just-completed trip to the soviet union. during the talks in moscow, shultz and soviet foreign minister eduard shevardnadze set a one-month deadline for arms negotiators to complete drafts on key elements of a new treaty to curb strategic nuclear weapons
