someone is going to give him a macho award for beating up on a young girl who has already been abused,'' sharpton said of cuomo
according to sharpton, the brawleys and their advisers continue to seek assurances that abrams will be personally involved in the investigation and trial of the case. in addition, he said the family remains troubled by what he maintains is the ``special relationship'' between abrams and dutchess county sheriff frederick scoralick, who one newspaper has reported as being implicated in the case by miss brawley
